result.adr_address: 17 Wai Ching St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 17 Wai Ching St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Funky Monkey

reviews.text:
This is a great place! Love the Nepalese atmosphere and food. The staff is great and the owner delightful and full of surprises. Good live music on Saturdays... Well I'm only here for a short while but it's basically been my HQ for 2 weeks now. Come and see for yourselves.
You have to try (and love 😘) the momo ( Nepalese dumplings)! They're the best!
Decent prices and a giant projected screen for sports
Can not be recommended, to expensive for nothing. I really feel cheated with a bad service.
Absolutely amazing food, a great place to go for group meals and they do wonderful cocktails. The papya salad was delicious as was the Momo. My favourite was the lotus flower dish.
Chilled spot out of the way. Great for friends to get together
